&lt;p&gt;At Loka, the work we do has cut billions in food waste, helped children around the world learn to read, and supported everything from barbershop apps to cancer research. Since 2023 alone, we&#39;ve helped launch more than 500 AI projects for bold startups and household brands. We&#39;re the &lt;strong&gt;AWS Innovation Partner of the Year&lt;/strong&gt;, and we&#39;ve built an award-winning marketing engine that&#39;s helping move the services industry forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All of this, and we still enjoy every other Friday off of work (yes, really).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&#39;s the broad pitch. Now let&#39;s talk about you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m the CMO and I&#39;m looking for a Senior Content &amp;amp; Communications Lead who is an exceptional writer, sharp thinker, and obsessive about clarity. This is a &lt;strong&gt;hands-on senior IC role&lt;/strong&gt;. You&#39;ll own our content end-to-end — long-form, short-form, sales enablement copy, web, email, and narrative assets that shape how Loka is perceived by AWS sellers, buyers, and the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll partner closely with me at first, then within 6 months be trusted to ship externally without oversight, make confident editorial calls, and raise the quality of every piece of communication that goes out under Loka&#39;s name.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a role for someone who wants to wait to be told what to write for a year. I&#39;m looking for someone who deeply understands what we do, who we serve, and how we win — and turns that understanding into sharp, accurate, audience-ready writing. Someone who takes a vague brief and comes back with a structured plan. Someone who can sit on a call with an engineer, a client, or an AWS AM and translate what they heard into content that actually lands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background in engineering, cloud, software, services, or B2B tech is essential.&lt;/strong&gt; Loka is a full-stack software consultancy — we build production AI, agentic systems, cloud migrations, and data platforms for regulated industries. The best version of this role is filled by someone who already speaks the language: a former engineer who moved into content, a writer who has spent years at a cloud/AI/SaaS company, an editor who covered enterprise tech, or someone who grew up in B2B services. Engineering background is the strongest plus. If you&#39;ve only written about consumer brands or lifestyle topics, this isn&#39;t the right fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m looking for someone with the rigor to translate technical substance into content that lands. You ask sharp questions. You explain your choices. You care about audience and objective as much as craft. You should also be deeply fluent in how content and marketing are evolving. You can talk clearly about how you&#39;re using AI and agents to scale your work, where those tools create leverage, and where human judgment still matters most. We move fast at Loka, but we do it sustainably. We care about long-term growth in our team and business, not short-term burnout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re nodding along enthusiastically, I&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Original Content &amp;amp; External Communications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and produce high-impact external content — case studies, web pages, landing copy, sales emails, offers, social posts, thought leadership, campaign narratives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate Loka&#39;s technical wins (GenAI, agentic systems, cloud migrations, regulated-industry deployments) into sharp, accurate, audience-ready writing that lands with AWS sellers and buyers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain the working understanding of Loka&#39;s offerings,

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Loka&lt;/strong&gt; we use a modern tech stack to support meaningful projects across a huge range of industries. In the last year our teams have helped clients advance the world&#39;s #1 AI reading tutor, eliminate $1B in food waste and develop novel drugs for fighting cancer, all while enjoying every other Friday off. Join us, feed your need to grow and ship projects you believe in with a team you&#39;re proud to be a part of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking a &lt;strong&gt;DevOps Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to deploy, secure and maintain robust applications in production environments, mainly AWS. The ideal candidate will not only apply their technical brilliance but also take a leadership role in contributing positively to Loka&#39;s unique culture.&lt;/p&gt;
