&lt;li&gt;Lead high-complexity projects with high-priority clients, independently resolve critical technical issues and introduce innovative solutions that ensure long-term maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape technical strategies, anticipate future trends, align initiatives with key business outcomes and drive execution across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
