&lt;li&gt;Set clear expectations for quality, scope ownership and proactive partnership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach team members on complex cases - performance management, organizational change, manager capability and employee relations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a consistent team operating model that balances regional autonomy with global coherence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify capability gaps and drive development across the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic HRBP Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the senior HRBP for specific senior leaders or business areas, depending on organizational needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the HR Director to translate business priorities into people strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive or co-own global HR initiatives across performance, compensation and manager effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Challenge and support senior leaders with honest, well-reasoned people counsel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
